    "nw_pdp_accordion": {
      "type": "nw-product-accordion",
      "blocks": {
        "acc_1": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Product Overview",
            "content": "<p>This premium outdoor sauna combines Canadian Hemlock wood with industry-leading Harvia heating technology. Designed for 4 persons and built for year-round use, it delivers a superior sauna experience from the comfort of your own backyard. Heavy-duty construction, full insulation, and thoughtful design details make this one of the finest outdoor saunas available.</p>"
          }
        },
        "acc_2": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why This Product Stands Out",
            "content": "<p>Unlike mass-produced saunas, every unit is crafted with thick 2×6 tongue-and-groove wall panels for superior insulation, a tempered glass door and panoramic windows, and a roof structure engineered to handle heavy snow loads. The result is a sauna that performs beautifully in every climate, looks stunning in any backyard, and is built to last decades.</p>"
          }
        },
        "acc_3": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What’s Included",
            "content": "<p>Your sauna kit includes: pre-cut and pre-drilled tongue-and-groove wall panels, a tempered glass entry door, panoramic tempered glass side windows, a two-tier bench system, roof panels and shingles, a Harvia 6kW heater, all mounting hardware and fasteners, an illustrated assembly guide, and a sauna stone set.</p>"
          }
        },
        "acc_4": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Specifications",
            "content": "<p><strong>Capacity:</strong> 4 persons<br><strong>Exterior dimensions:</strong> 96″ W × 96″ D × 96″ H<br><strong>Interior dimensions:</strong> 84″ W × 84″ D × 84″ H<br><strong>Ceiling height:</strong> 7’ (84″)<br><strong>Wall thickness:</strong> 1.75″<br><strong>Wood species:</strong> Canadian Hemlock<br><strong>Heater power:</strong> 240V / 60A / 6kW Harvia Vega<br><strong>Sauna stones weight:</strong> 20 lbs included<br><strong>Shipping weight:</strong> approx. 1,200 lbs</p>"
          }
        },
        "acc_5": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Assembly & Installation",
            "content": "<p>The sauna ships approximately 90% pre-assembled and can typically be set up by 2 adults in 4–6 hours using basic tools (drill, level, wrench). A flat, level surface is required — concrete pad, pavers, compacted gravel, or a deck all work great. The heater requires a dedicated 240V / 60A GFCI circuit, installed by a licensed electrician.</p>"
          }
        },
        "acc_6": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Upgrades & Add-Ons",
            "content": "<p>Personalize your sauna experience with available upgrades: LED chromotherapy lighting strips (under-bench and behind backrest), decorative hexagon panels for the back wall, and premium cold plunge bundles for post-sauna cold therapy. Select your preferred options at the top of this page using the swatch pickers.</p>"
          }
        },
        "acc_7": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Shipping and Delivery",
            "content": "<p>Ships free nationwide via LTL freight directly to your home. Estimated delivery is 2–4 weeks from order date. You will receive a tracking number once your order ships, and the freight carrier will call to schedule a delivery appointment at a time that works for you. Liftgate service is included.</p>"
          }
        },
        "acc_8": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Warranty",
            "content": "<p>As an Authorized Dealer, we fully back every unit sold:<br><strong>5-year</strong> structural warranty on the wood frame<br><strong>2-year</strong> warranty on the Harvia heater<br><strong>1-year</strong> parts and hardware warranty<br>We handle all warranty claims directly — no runaround, no hassle. Contact our team at any time and we will make it right.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
